Timedevel application. Small task/time manager. Prevents wasting time on
unimportant activities.

***
DEV INFO

1. MVC patern in timedevel app:

                        CONTROLER
                        +-------------------+
                        |  Timedevel        |
                        |-------------------|
             +----------+-m_taskManager     |
             |          |                   |
             |          |-m_mainWindow +------------------------+
             |          |                   |                   |
             |          |-m_focusDetector   |                   |
             |          +-------------------+                   |
MODEL        |              timedevel.h/cpp                     |
+------------+---------+                            VIEW        |
|    TaskManager       |                            +-----------+--------+
|----------------------|                            |    MainWindow      |
|+add(Task)            |         SIGNALS            |--------------------|
|+remove(Task)         |<---------------------------+                    |
|...                   |                            |GUI                 |
|                      |                            |                    |
|-writeToFile()        |                            |-m_taskView:QTreeWid|
|-readFromFile()       |                            |                    |
|...                   |                            |                    |
|                      |                            |                    |
+----------------------+                            +--------------------+
  taskmanager.h/cpp                                    mainwindow.h/cpp

